@optional {frequency: num # Defines the number of days between each scan (0 = One-off scan)., ports: [str] # Defines a list of ports to scan. Valid values are:"default", "all", or a comma-separated list of ports or range of ports (e.g. ["1-80", "443"]). "default" scans the 100 most commonly open ports.}
