@optional {page_token: str # Opaque pagination token from a previous response. Use this to fetch the next page of results., page_size: int=100 # Maximum number of tables to return per page. Defaults to 100, maximum 1000., return_uuids: bool=False # Whether to include table UUIDs in the response. Set to true to receive the table_uuids array., return_details: bool=False # Whether to include additional metadata (timestamps, locations). When true, response includes created_at, updated_at, metadata_locations, and locations arrays.}
@returns(200) List of tables retrieved successfully.
@errors {400: Bad request (e.g., invalid page_size, malformed namespace)., 401: Authentication failed., 403: Forbidden., 404: Catalog or namespace not found., 500: Internal server error.}

